Features
--------

- Ticker display
- Sell bitcoins
- Buy bitcoins
- Cancel orders


Run
---

Just call
	php tickerCoins.php
on the console.

On Windows make sure you have the php executable in your PATH.

On Mac you have to set the "date.timezone" value in the php.ini as admin.


